Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.15,0:00:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.95,0:00:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万万没想到这么快收到你的短信
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.29,0:00:15.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.02,0:00:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么  想做模特了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.60,0:00:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.95,0:00:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…今后也能约二鸟君一起玩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.93,0:00:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.56,0:00:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.78,0:00:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,专程来问我这件事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.99,0:00:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.11,0:00:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事都放在心上真是个循规蹈矩的人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.91,0:00:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小乃  快来吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.96,0:00:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  肯定没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.90,0:00:50.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定  都没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.72,0:01:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.80,0:01:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好…我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.09,0:01:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今天开始换春装了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.93,0:01:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是  你也穿错了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.02,0:01:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.41,0:01:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以了

Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.41,0:02:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.53,0:02:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.42,0:02:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.16,0:03:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.43,0:03:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是三年级的老师  没被发现呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.96,0:03:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.09,0:03:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧张吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.49,0:03:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然会
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.28,0:03:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边的同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.86,0:03:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同学你这领结是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.75,0:03:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘记啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.58,0:03:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Safe
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.12,0:03:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.02,0:03:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.05,0:03:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这身打扮是什么  好帅！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.89,0:03:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太显眼太显眼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.15,0:03:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好帅好帅好帅！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.02,0:03:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高槻  没想到你也被更科传染了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.61,0:03:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是觉得这样穿是帅气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.87,0:03:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  哪怕只是被认为在模仿小千
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.18,0:03:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兼田老师来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.84,0:03:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  日志？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.94,0:03:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.96,0:04:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是女生吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.39,0:04:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.13,0:04:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这身是特地买的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.02,0:04:08.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是别人送的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.92,0:04:11.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌女生的制服吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.30,0:04:15.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…也不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.83,0:04:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  是讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.48,0:04:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒  这下还真成了高槻君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.07,0:04:31.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过真的好帅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.05,0:04:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.77,0:04:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.13,0:04:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千叶同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.32,0:04:45.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也没吃惊  那人就喜欢小题大做
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.00,0:04:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  小千…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.38,0:04:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衣领
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.31,0:04:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.45,0:05:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是觉得二鸟和高槻同学挺般配的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.28,0:05:04.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也觉得她很帅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.52,0:05:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.67,0:05:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二鸟君
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.09,0:05:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高…高槻同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.10,0:05:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.48,0:05:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千叶同学告诉我你可能在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.70,0:05:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.32,0:05:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二鸟君  我们约会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.11,0:05:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.81,0:05:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说约会有些不太妥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.03,0:05:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换个说法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.50,0:05:37.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不介意的话再一起去雪姐家玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.11,0:05:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下周日有时间吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.39,0:05:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天有点不方便
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.28,0:05:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了  那下次再约
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.25,0:05:51.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的好帅哟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.09,0:05:56.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到了安那的同意真是让人敬佩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.77,0:05:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好帅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.16,0:06:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很帅…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.88,0:06:11.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安那吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.11,0:06:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.83,0:06:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The sun was bright in the blue sky
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.99,0:06:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but the boy could not see it
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.95,0:06:26.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能做什么的「can」的过去式是「could」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.05,0:06:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}（我是土居  想见一下上次的大姐姐）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.15,0:06:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为什么 或者是想做什么的「will」过去形式是「would」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.94,0:06:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须要做什么 肯定是什么时 需要加上「must」…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.37,0:06:35.67,SPEC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs18\fad(400,400)}土居：可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.33,0:06:38.67,SPEC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18\fad(400,400)}修一：你怎么知道我的邮箱地址的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.29,0:06:46.55,SPEC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs18\fad(400,0)}土居：从你姐姐那
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.34,0:06:46.55,SPEC2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs18\fad(400,0)}我们两个的姐姐是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.55,0:06:50.80,SPEC3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}土居：下周日  怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.71,0:06:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  一点左右到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.88,0:06:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  雪姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.81,0:06:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  带他过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.14,0:07:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过要多防着他哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.91,0:07:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  谢谢  一会见
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.73,0:07:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.86,0:07:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟来做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.88,0:07:24.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.74,0:07:26.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是二鸟君的保镖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.17,0:07:28.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么保镖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.38,0:07:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你傻啊  明明是个女的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.98,0:07:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.62,0:07:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么  难道你们真的在交往
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.53,0:07:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二鸟已经有女朋友了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.99,0:07:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.27,0:07:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然有女朋友还让她保护你做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.69,0:07:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱…抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.45,0:07:58.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.90,0:08:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.16,0:08:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找我这个人妖姐姐有什么事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.57,0:08:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没什么特别的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.82,0:08:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.02,0:08:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人妖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.94,0:08:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是以前是男人的意思哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.99,0:08:16.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.93,0:08:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小西  快起来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.29,0:08:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好困
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.23,0:08:23.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有客人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.86,0:08:28.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不但是人妖  还和这人一起住
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.37,0:08:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.03,0:08:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说吧  有什么事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.77,0:08:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  只是觉得你很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.32,0:08:48.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…究竟是什么来头？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.53,0:08:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会是黑帮的儿子之类的厉害角色吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.94,0:09:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交友圈这么特殊到底怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.13,0:09:07.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打电话给雪姐  说二鸟君要过来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.07,0:09:08.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.32,0:09:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能对土居唯命是从啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.82,0:09:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.81,0:09:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…我能问个奇怪问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.73,0:09:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.53,0:09:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次见到的内衣  买了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.86,0:09:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  现在也穿着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.89,0:09:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会觉得太紧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.41,0:09:37.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会  反而感觉轻松些
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.52,0:09:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻松些吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.85,0:09:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.97,0:09:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是心情的原因吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.07,0:09:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.63,0:09:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你的赞美
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.06,0:10:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.81,0:10:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本是男人的美女真让人不敢想像
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.94,0:10:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.38,0:10:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打扮成女生看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.63,0:10:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.13,0:10:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么  只是想看看而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.12,0:10:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土居
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.29,0:10:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.39,0:10:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放学一起回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.45,0:10:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数学书借我下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.84,0:10:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你又没带啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.23,0:10:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.89,0:10:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.60,0:10:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不用担心我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.05,0:10:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明早将会在新的街角…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.45,0:10:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的你如同一只小鹿蹒跚而行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.67,0:10:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.74,0:10:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说千叶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.20,0:10:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里应该是「像小鹿一样步伐轻盈」才对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.15,0:10:52.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.21,0:10:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.31,0:10:59.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会心跳加速
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.48,0:11:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.98,0:11:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.47,0:11:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.42,0:11:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天去拍摄了  估计会很晚回来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.77,0:11:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊  我可以进去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.54,0:11:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.09,0:11:46.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.62,0:11:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说这是什么  假发吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.40,0:11:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.67,0:12:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就穿成这样去学校吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.59,0:12:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高槻不是都穿得像个男生吗
Comment: 0,0:00:01.80,0:00:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.17,0:12:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真穗  记得把明天的东西整理好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.49,0:12:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.40,0:12:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.40,0:12:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去爷爷家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.60,0:12:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  麻烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.12,0:12:42.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说话的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.03,0:12:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修也觉得很麻烦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.21,0:12:47.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是还好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.74,0:12:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.97,0:12:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦  麻烦  麻烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.21,0:12:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要说这种话啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.55,0:12:57.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.90,0:12:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到你和姐姐约好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.94,0:13:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用介意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.40,0:13:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在还会打扮成女孩子的样子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.02,0:13:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不怎么做了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.00,0:13:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.28,0:13:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惹你姐姐生气了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.95,0:13:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我经常惹姐姐生气
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.88,0:13:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人很容易生气
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.67,0:13:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.17,0:13:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.36,0:13:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真穗和修
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.53,0:13:33.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.17,0:13:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎哟  两个女生真是美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.53,0:13:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们家都是男孩子  很无聊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.18,0:13:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.29,0:13:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我把花拿去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.58,0:13:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  再见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.79,0:13:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那个人是奥山太太
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.41,0:13:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我们一起学习插花
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.05,0:13:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是升级贺礼的还礼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.60,0:13:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你们特地来一趟  真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.69,0:14:01.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝果汁还是红茶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.11,0:14:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.11,0:14:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果还是在这里住下了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.80,0:14:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天还有摄影
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.46,0:14:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上还要回家  几点起来好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.14,0:14:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什么爱好？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.83,0:14:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.96,0:14:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听什么样的音乐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.06,0:14:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么特别的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.97,0:14:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是姐姐放歌的时候一起听
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.95,0:14:30.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游戏呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.21,0:14:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不玩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.08,0:14:36.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的兴趣果然是扮女生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.78,0:14:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像你以前在日记里写过这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.81,0:14:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高槻同学变帅了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.76,0:14:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想像高槻同学一样…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.71,0:15:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像高槻同学一样…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.62,0:15:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二鸟居然一个人来真是稀奇呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.71,0:15:24.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.54,0:15:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为家里一个人都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.41,0:15:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.95,0:15:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千一直都在店里帮忙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.89,0:15:36.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  我可是招牌女孩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.82,0:15:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  问了奇怪的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.14,0:15:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二鸟大概会很合适吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.54,0:15:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是会不会被欺负呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.46,0:15:49.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然小千也这么认为吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.98,0:15:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.18,0:15:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男孩子要这么打扮难度实在太高
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.52,0:16:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不能穿裙子呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.21,0:16:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只怕会被当成变态吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.08,0:16:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒也不是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.85,0:16:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有很多人觉得奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.28,0:16:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想被人家说奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.03,0:16:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到小千…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.41,0:16:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.70,0:16:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然会想那么多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.45,0:16:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  也就是说你把小千当白痴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.55,0:16:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.00,0:16:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得我是变态吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.72,0:16:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.09,0:16:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过二鸟很的确很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.68,0:16:42.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢…谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.50,0:16:44.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然不反驳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.20,0:16:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不喜欢二鸟以这种方式突出自己  会有坏影响
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.38,0:16:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不推荐你穿成那样去上学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.61,0:16:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但决定权不在我手上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.89,0:17:03.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.67,0:17:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果可以的话…我会马上还的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.63,0:17:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是没有什么问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.15,0:17:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但为什么突然又要借女生制服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.38,0:17:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明天想穿着去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.26,0:17:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿着去？去学校吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.32,0:17:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是土居吗  是土居吧  那个混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.49,0:17:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊  你不能听他的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.43,0:17:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道他跟你说什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.17,0:17:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽…虽然不能说和土居完全没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.94,0:17:43.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但只是一个契机罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.71,0:17:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和他没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.39,0:17:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不知道会被人家说成什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.73,0:17:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是高槻同学不是打扮成男生上学吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.97,0:17:59.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高槻同学不是没被说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.24,0:18:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕  听着像在挖苦她
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.83,0:18:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐会不会请假不去学校啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.46,0:18:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那样  我就可以穿着去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.28,0:18:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但要是露馅了  她又要生气
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.54,0:18:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是肯定的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.21,0:18:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件衣服已经很久没穿了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.71,0:18:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.43,0:18:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.66,0:18:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.79,0:18:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.11,0:18:35.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.62,0:18:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是安那给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.81,0:18:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得很可爱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.72,0:18:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是要配成一对  真傻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.86,0:18:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想和高槻同学一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.17,0:19:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,释放自己
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.94,0:19:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈大概会大吃一惊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.07,0:19:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸大概也会像姐姐一样生气吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.30,0:19:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么啊  盯着人家看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.21,0:19:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能这么说话哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.37,0:19:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法  我性格扭曲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.30,0:19:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开口闭口都是这句话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.22,0:19:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这是真的嘛  没办法啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.85,0:19:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己说有些不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.26,0:19:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在座的应该数我最沉着冷静吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.33,0:19:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说这句话的人好像是小诚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.62,0:19:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过也无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.47,0:19:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很紧张  我已经决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.18,0:19:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.40,0:19:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.69,0:19:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.69,0:19:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.40,0:19:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.56,0:20:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转校生？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.15,0:20:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二…二鸟？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.56,0:20:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…和他好像
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.45,0:20:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我就是二鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.95,0:20:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.48,0:20:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.65,0:20:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二鸟修一
Comment: 0,0:00:02.50,0:00:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.72,0:22:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可真是震惊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.26,0:22:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都吓了一跳  我也不例外
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.69,0:22:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是二鸟  真的很合适  我有点羡慕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.80,0:22:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.76,0:22:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的真的  穿着水手服来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.98,0:22:43.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果还是被拉到保健室里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.09,0:22:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后他妈妈赶来把他带了回去


